get.description:
Returns a JSON listing for the folder provided with the 'id' param. This will be the ID with the following sub properties, with the defaults set: 


name = ""; 
id = ""; 
createdDate = -1; 
createdBy = ""; 
modifiedDate = -1;
modifiedBy = ""; 
type = ""; 
baseType = ""; 
simflofyType = "";
contentLength = -1; 
mimeType = ""; 
description = ""; 
checkinComment = "";
versionCount = -1; 
itemPath = "";
